name: Cavaleras - Big Mama
description:
Hand woodcut work, on the theme of Mexican Cavaleras. 

I love the object of the nesting dolls, discovering new ones is always a pleasure and an excitement to discover the very last one.

So I wanted to create some from my personal universe, and the idea of ​​death is one of the things I like to play with in my work. It's a way to ward off an obession. But I have others: D
